{"id": "1454065867045339156", "channel_id": "1454065867045339156", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n       弥萨格大学校务处将于12月26日19:10(UTC+8) 进行校内设施修复，更新完成后您将得到通知，重新进入游戏。对于更新可能给大家带来的不便，我们会准备一份补给物资以示歉意。祝大家调查顺利！ \n  \n【补给物资】\n在线维护补偿：银芯×50\n  \n【领取条件】\n领取时间截至2026年1月9日23:59。请记得及时前往邮箱领取补给物资哦。  \n \n【更新内容】\n一、活动\n【纪念活动：因雾之名】\n● 在 12 月 29 日 9:00 - 1 月 26 日 9:00 期间，以下活动限时开放！\n    ○ 通关「调查行动-忘却篇-第一章」即可免费领取当期限定唤醒体「茉夏」。\n    ○ 因雾之名，她将跨越门扉，与你再度邂逅！\n \n二、问题修复\n● 修复了「战斗」中多个敌人同时被唤醒体「艾继丝」施加「石化」状态时，「石化」的特效表现会丢失的问题。\n● 修复了「战斗」中血肉界域能力「猩红熔炉」在使用确认时回复数值未正确显示的问题。\n● 修复了「探索」中部分剧情事件节点会卡死的问题。\n● 修复了「相位对弈」中命轮「沉入殷红」的失去生命条件不正确而无法触发的问题。\n● 修复了「兑换码」不能正确兑换，总是错误的提示存在非法字符的问题。\n● 修复了「唤醒」中进行「无垢之芯」和「流明之芯」兑换时显示的道具数量错误为 1000 的问题。\n● 修复了在网络延迟较高时，可能会频繁出现网络连接提示的问题。", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T10:58:37.941000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1454065867255058564", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131426, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1454065867045339156/1454065867255058564/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=69cc519d&is=69cb001d&hm=10b9aa90dfdd44709fbf386bbbdf1c2c760946cb8fb49f3c2c448b0ab9a7d2bc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454065867045339156", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.1.1 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1454065926323568705", "channel_id": "1454065867045339156", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "**V2.4.1.1 Online Maintenance Announcement**\n\nDear Keeper,\nThe Mythag Administration Office will conduct campus facility maintenance on December 26 at 19:10(UTC+8) . You will be notified once the update is complete and you can re-enter the game. As an apology for any inconvenience caused by the update, we will provide a supply package. Wishing everyone a successful investigation!\n \n[Compensation]\nOnline Maintenance Compensation: Silver×50\n \n[Claim Conditions]\nThe claiming time ends on January 9, 2026 at 23:59. Please remember to go to your mailox in time to claim the supply materials.\n \n[Update Content]\n1. Event\n[Memorial Event: In the Name of Fog]\n● From December 29 at 9:00 to January 26 at 9:00, the following events are available for a limited time!\n○ Clear \"Investigation - Faded Legacy - Chapter One\" to receive the current limited Awakener \"Mouchette\" for free.\n○ In the name of the fog, she will cross the gateway and encounter you once again!\n\n2. Problem Fix\n● Fixed an issue where the petrification effect would be lost when multiple enemies were simultaneously Petrified by the Awakener \"Aigis\" in battle.\n● Fixed the issue where the healing value for the Caro Realm ability \"Crimson Furnace\" did not display correctly when confirming usage in \"Battle.\"\n● Fixed the issue where some storyline event nodes in \"Exploration\" would freeze.\n● Fixed the issue in \"Traphase\" where the Wheel of Destiny \"Drowning in Crimson\" had incorrect HP loss conditions that prevented activation.\n● Fixed the issue where the \"redemption code\" could not be redeemed correctly, always displaying an error message about invalid characters.\n● Fixed the issue where the item quantity displayed during the exchange of \"Pure Core\" and \"Luminous Core\" in \"Awaken\" was incorrectly shown as 1000.\n● Fixed an issue where network connection prompts could frequently appear during high network latency.", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T10:58:52.074000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🩶", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454065867045339156", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.1.1 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
