{"id": "1453943478001078334", "channel_id": "1453726962899091498", "type": 19, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@233217233583734785>After my inquiry, the answer I received was this🙏 Perhaps the programmer discovered the issue after further verification, but did not synchronize with me.\nThese questions are all feedback to the production team, I cannot fabricate answers. There are many bugs that need to be addressed every day, and sometimes there may be issues with information synchronization misalignment.", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T02:52:18.119000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["233217233583734785"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1453756194455027837", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1453726962899091498", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1453947971736703177", "channel_id": "1453726962899091498", "type": 19, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@233217233583734785><@330867601691639809><@645758482305253422><@1437487264023318668>Just communicated with the project team, 'Some bosses have a mechanism to not clear their summarized monsters when they die' - this is indeed the initial mechanism.\nLater on, they considered optimizing this mechanism - adjusting it to the result stated in the announcement. But this change was not synchronized with me, so I replied to everyone like that at that time.\n\nI will translate every feedback from everyone into Chinese and organize it clearly for the project team. There is no need for me to spend so much energy on providing feedback and then fabricate a response. This is also an extremely irresponsible behavior for everyone and the project team. I will not do this.\nIn the future, I will confirm the bug handling results with the project team multiple times to avoid similar issues from happening.", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:10:09.509000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["645758482305253422", "233217233583734785", "1437487264023318668", "330867601691639809"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "Jointhefun2", "emoji_id": "1400771643743408210", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1453766578268012544", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1453726962899091498", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
